ing on the density\nstructure in the common gap. This is illustrated for the Kepler-46 system, for\nwhich we reproduce the period ratio of Kepler-46b and c.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Jan 2013 17:45:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 18 May 2013 14:32:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2013 08:00:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
