els. First-infall orbits are preferred (as\nsupported by other arguments as well) if one imposes the requirement that the\nLMC and SMC must have been a bound pair for at least several Gyr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Jan 2013 21:01:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
